{"tid":91211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩有位巴打跳樓死左","createTime":"2017-01-22T16:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T17:58:31.000Z","uid":58099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fbe36063307f73c924ff353d0ee5f7a3db589aea","tid":91211,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/23/000908_410bb88d202dd7971f45997858e3b4ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F23%2F000908_410bb88d202dd7971f45997858e3b4ae.jpg&h=68f169e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃大仙翠竹花園一單位，傍晚6時許，一名19歲姓林青年從第7座一單位高處墮下，倒臥天井位置，救護員到場證實男子當場死亡，警方到場後用綠帆布蓋住遺體，其後上樓搜查，最後成功聯絡其家人，確認他在中層單位一個廁所窗口一躍而下。警方在現場未撿獲遺書，但相信事件無可疑，遺體抬走交法醫確認死因。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，姓林青年今日將自己鎖在睡房內，其後突然走入廁所，家人未幾聽到樓下傳來一聲巨響，方知林跳樓身亡。消息稱，林性格內向，中學畢業後一直待業至今，生前曽於網上透露不開心，警方不排除他一時看不開自尋短見。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想今個星期六等屋企人出曬街之後跳樓<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/87086/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/87086/page/1?ref=ios</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"35f91b32b31025e2daf936cf8cee6deb859e2d87","tid":91211,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f6184257ed91a603196d04df055e046584e128","tid":91211,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:20:36.000Z","msg":"記者朋友好 我係Donald侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf77634a443c5d209a70dd65a218cb397ff808fe","tid":91211,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:22:18.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"2ad8d1057f4e1827cb3e5412ed119ff418b275a4","tid":91211,"uid":69256,"like":0,"dislike"